</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-52_ pf-text-1"><strong>Clear emergency plans </strong>- Have clear, written plans that are easily accessible and include specific steps to take in the event of various types of emergencies.





















